categories: Category:Star Wars: The Clone Wars voice actors

nodes.text: Kathryn Ann "Katee" Sackhoff (born April 8, 1980) is an American actress who voices former Death Watch lieutenant-turned Mandalorian loyalist Bo-Katan Kryze for the fourth, fifth, and seventh seasons of Star Wars: The Clone Wars, as well as the fourth season of Star Wars Rebels. She also portrays the character in live-action in the second season of The Mandalorian. She is best known for her role as Kara "Starbuck" Thrace on the Sci Fi Channel's television program Battlestar Galactica.
